<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Because he feels overwhelmed and scared and lost and wishes he had his daddy back. He&apos;s grieving and depressed and adding fame onto it makes him feel <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Because he feels overwhelmed and scared and lost and wishes he had his daddy back. He's grieving and depressed and adding fame onto it makes him feel like he is a child again who is lost and doesn't know what to do. imo.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
