<span id="freeTextContainer6274113194300034377"><b>Art Spiegelman</b> (born <b>Itzhak Avraham ben Zeev</b>) is New-York-based comics artist, editor, and advocate for the medium of comics, best known for his Pulitzer Prize-winning comic memoir, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15195.Maus' rel='nofollow noopener'>Maus</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText6274113194300034377" style="display:none"><b>Art Spiegelman</b> (born <b>Itzhak Avraham ben Zeev</b>) is New-York-based comics artist, editor, and advocate for the medium of comics, best known for his Pulitzer Prize-winning comic memoir, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15195.Maus" rel="nofollow noopener">Maus</a>.</span>
